---
/**
 * ProcessSection Component
 *
 * Displays the 3-step turnkey process:
 * 1. You send your content
 * 2. We translate and validate
 * 3. You receive in 48h
 *
 * Features:
 * - Semantic HTML with ARIA landmarks
 * - Responsive design: 1 col mobile, 3 col desktop
 * - Inline SVG icons for visual impact
 * - Reassurance message: "You don't have to manage anything"
 * - WCAG AA compliant color contrast
 */

interface Props {
  // No props needed for MVP - hard-coded content
}
---

<section
  id="process"
  aria-labelledby="process-heading"
  aria-label="Processus de travail"
  class="py-16 md:py-24 px-6 md:px-12 bg-white"
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Section Heading -->
    <h2 id="process-heading" class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center text-neutral-900 mb-12">
      Notre Processus Clé-en-Main
    </h2>

    <!-- 3-Step Process Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-12">

      <!-- Step 1: You send -->
      <div class="text-center space-y-4">
        <div class="text-6xl font-bold text-accent-500 mb-4">
          <span class="sr-only">Étape </span>
          <span aria-hidden="true">1</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <!-- Document Icon - Clear visual for "send your content" -->
          <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-primary-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900">
          Vous envoyez votre contenu
        </p>
        <p class="text-base text-neutral-700">
          Aucune conversion requise - envoyez tel quel, tout format accepté.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2: We translate and validate -->
      <div class="text-center space-y-4">
        <div class="text-6xl font-bold text-accent-500 mb-4">
          <span class="sr-only">Étape </span>
          <span aria-hidden="true">2</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <!-- Globe/Language Icon -->
          <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-primary-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900">
          On traduit et valide
        </p>
        <p class="text-base text-neutral-700">
          Aucune relecture à faire - validation par experts natifs incluse.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3: You receive in 48h -->
      <div class="text-center space-y-4">
        <div class="text-6xl font-bold text-accent-500 mb-4">
          <span class="sr-only">Étape </span>
          <span aria-hidden="true">3</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-center">
          <!-- Check Circle Icon -->
          <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-primary-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900">
          Vous recevez en 48h
        </p>
        <p class="text-base text-neutral-700">
          Aucune intégration technique - livraison en 48h, prêt à publier.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Reassurance Message -->
    <div class="mt-16 text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-accent-100 border-2 border-accent-300 rounded-lg hover:scale-105 focus-within:scale-105 transition-transform">
        <!-- Check Shield Icon for reassurance -->
        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
        </svg>
        <span class="text-xl font-bold text-accent-700">
          Vous n'avez rien à gérer - On s'occupe de tout
        </span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
